if I never see her again.

786
00:47:59,192 --> 00:48:01,251
Will you go to the prom with me?

787
00:48:01,461 --> 00:48:03,019
After she declined?
No, thanks.

788
00:48:03,230 --> 00:48:05,824
But I'm glad she did, because
now I can ask you.

789
