912
00:56:11,567 --> 00:56:12,864
Have fun.

913
00:56:21,944 --> 00:56:23,172
Goodbye.

914
00:56:39,762 --> 00:56:44,699
I thought I'd found my ideal man

915
00:56:45,401 --> 00:56:50,236
I always knew he'd arrive

916
00:56:50,973 --> 00:56:55,910
